The paper deals with lane detection in autonomous driving, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method also involves deep learning models, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions post-processing techniques, which could fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) if they involve text analysis.
